## Google Reviews (Maps JavaScript API + Places)
## 1) Create an API key in Google Cloud
## 2) Enable "Maps JavaScript API" (and Places)
## 3) Restrict the key by HTTP referrer for your domain
VITE_GOOGLE_MAPS_API_KEY=

## Your Google Place ID (for Café Keppler)
VITE_GOOGLE_PLACE_ID=

## Resend (contact, sollicitatie, bakkerij, groepen)
## Set RESEND_API_KEY (+ optional RESEND_FROM) in Vercel: Project → Settings → Environment Variables
## Staff inbox for all forms is fixed in code: api/mailConfig.ts (BUSINESS_INBOX)
## RESEND_FROM: use any address @ your verified domain (e.g. noreply@cafekeppler.nl)
RESEND_API_KEY=
RESEND_FROM=Café Keppler <noreply@cafekeppler.nl>


